fr.inria.atlanmod.mogwai.neoemf.resource

Interface MogwaiResource

  • All Superinterfaces:
    AutoCloseable, Closeable, Notifier, PersistentResource, Resource, Resource.Internal
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultMogwaiResource, MogwaiResourceDecorator

    public interface MogwaiResource
extends PersistentResource
    Extends the PersistentResource interface with Mogwai query capabilities.

    The provided API allows to query and transform a PersistentResource using MogwaiQuery objects.

    Author:
    Gwendal DANIEL

    • Method Detail

      • transform

        NeoEMFQueryResult transform(MogwaiQuery transformation,
                            Map<String,Object> options)
                     throws QueryException
        Computes the provided transformation with the given options.

        The provided transformation is computed in-place, meaning that the underlying database storing the NeoEMF resource is directly updated with the result of the transformation. To compute a transformation that stores its output in another datastore see  transform(MogwaiQuery, Object, ModelDatastore, Map).

        Parameters:
        transformation - the MogwaiQuery representing the transformation to compute
        options - the execution options used to parameterize the underlying engine
        Returns:
        a NeoEMFQueryResult representing the result of the transformation execution
        Throws:
        QueryException - if the resource is not able to compute the provided query
        See Also:
        transform(MogwaiQuery, Object, ModelDatastore, Map)

      • transform

        <D> NeoEMFQueryResult transform(MogwaiQuery transformation,
                                D datastore,
                                ModelDatastore mapping,
                                Map<String,Object> options)
                         throws QueryException
        Computes the provided transformation with the provided options and stores its output in the given datastore according to the given mapping.

        The provided transformation is stored in the provided datastore, meaning that the underlying database storing the NeoEMF resource is not updated with the result of the transformation. To compute a transformation in-place see transform(MogwaiQuery, Map).

        Type Parameters:
        D - the datastore where to store the results of the transformation
        Parameters:
        transformation - the MogwaiQuery representing the transformation to compute
        datastore - the datastore containing the ouptut of the transformation
        mapping - the ModelDatastore used to access the ouput datastore
        options - the execution options used to parameterize the underlying engine
        Returns:
        a NeoEMFQueryResult representing the result of the transformation execution
        Throws:
        QueryException - if the resource is not able to compute the provided query
        See Also:
        transform(MogwaiQuery, Map)
